                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "execute unless entity @initiator[tag=defeated_villain_yield_analyst] run tbcs battle GEN_9_SINGLES @initiator vs villain_yield_analyst onwin {1: ['cobbledollars add @1 480', 'tag @1 add defeated_villain_yield_analyst', '@2 say Recorded. One loss, assessor. My confidence interval did not include you — which is itself a data point.'], 2: ['@2 say Engagement concluded. Your challenge has been logged as community sentiment, weight zero.']}"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Conditions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                    Operation: "NOT_EQUALS",
                                    Name: "defeated_villain_yield_analyst"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "contest_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Leave him to his refiling",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Update, for the record. Challenger traffic at this facility has moved the community valuation past the retention threshold. Greenspace 7 is refiled — brand asset, heritage class, retained. The garden stays."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I had the conversion at eighty percent likely. The numbers disagreed, and I answer to the numbers. You moved the numbers. Head office has authorized a goodwill disbursement, for the optics."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Analyst — the retained filing",
                    Label: "retained"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_villain_yield_analyst"
                        }
                    ],
                    Priority: 22,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Take the Yield Report from the dispatch tray",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "loot give @initiator loot cobblemon_initiative:npc_gift/rezoning_memo"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "tag @initiator add yield_report_taken"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "tag @initiator remove audit_loiter"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    Cmd: "tellraw @initiator [{\"text\":\"Yield Report RZ-7 secured. The analyst does not object. Lucian the archivist in Sango will want this.\",\"color\":\"gold\"}]"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Conditions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                    Operation: "NOT_EQUALS",
                                    Name: "yield_report_taken"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "tray_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Leave him to the forms",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The audit is suspended. Field incident, one loss, equipment intact. I have restated my findings as preliminary and my confidence as moderate."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The paperwork survives the auditor. It always does. The draft is in the dispatch tray if the community wants a copy. Evidence chooses its own custodian."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Analyst — audit suspended",
                    Label: "withdrawn"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "badges_gte_3"
                        }
                    ],
